{"tid":1040043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孩童增進大人幸福感？美國研究：取決於你有沒有錢","createTime":"2019-02-27T22:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T23:44:05.000Z","uid":122,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea7fb1a815924933ab6257c79e2382d85afac9da","tid":1040043,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:18:38.000Z","msg":"孩童總是為大人帶來歡樂？一項新研究卻顯示，歡樂的前提可能是父母必須「夠有錢」。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家經濟研究所（National Bureau of Economic Research）研究指出，當家長陷入財務困難時，孩童反而是造成不開心的因素；相反地，如果財務狀況不成問題，則孩童能增加家長們的幸福感。<br />\n<br />\n研究由達特茅斯學院（Dartmouth College）經濟學教授布蘭弗洛（David Blanchflower）和巴黎經濟學院（Paris School of Economics）教授克拉克（Andrew Clark）合力撰寫，分析從2009年至2018年，歐洲35國、100萬人口的生活滿意度調查。<br />\n<br />\n布蘭弗洛直白地說，殘酷事實擺在眼前，只是之前沒有人發現：「只有孩童沒有對你繳帳單造成困擾，他們才會讓父母更快樂。」（林孝儒／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"0ab2202365c7059715ba010498740ecc8df055f1","tid":1040043,"uid":179867,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:20:47.000Z","msg":"有錢唔一定快樂,但冇錢就一定唔快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1003d1625ba9f7bed5c2725c92aae8dc4c236f13","tid":1040043,"uid":37537,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:28:17.000Z","msg":"啲父母重成日賴係個仔唔生性令佢地唔開心<br />\n其實係佢地自己唔生性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f972d1a88acc09b7c82a53e098e8835d29a7d71","tid":1040043,"uid":22694,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:52:31.000Z","msg":"另一則報導：山係石頭海係水"},{"pid":"6eba1810d2d8608fbc0baf6e11db1d0de04e219b","tid":1040043,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T23:06:54.000Z","msg":"所以冇四百萬唔好生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0e362a8b418d24a03b8096b87a9219982121c8","tid":1040043,"uid":1255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6eba1810d2d8608fbc0baf6e11db1d0de04e219b","tid":1040043,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislik